---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

const pageTitle = "Hubungi Kami | Kontak Admin Cek Data Bocor";
const pageDescription = "Hubungi kontak resmi databocor.web.id jika Anda memiliki pertanyaan, masukan, kerja sama, atau laporan celah keamanan siber cek email dan akun hacker.";
---

<Layout title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription}>
  <Navbar />
  
  <main class="flex-grow py-12 px-4 bg-neutral-bg">
    <article class="max-w-xl mx-auto space-y-8">
      
      <!-- Judul Halaman -->
      <header class="space-y-2 border-b border-neutral-border pb-4 text-center sm:text-left">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-black text-neutral-text tracking-tight">
          Hubungi Kami
        </h1>
        <p class="text-sm text-neutral-textMuted">
          Kami sangat terbuka untuk pertanyaan, saran, atau kolaborasi
        </p>
      </header>

      <!-- Isi Halaman Kontak -->
      <section class="space-y-6 text-sm text-neutral-text leading-relaxed">
        <p class="text-center sm:text-left">
          Punya pertanyaan seputar kebocoran data, kritik, saran pengembangan website, atau ingin berkolaborasi? Jangan ragu untuk menghubungi kami langsung melalui kontak di bawah ini.
        </p>

        <!-- Kartu Kontak Premium -->
        <div class="bg-neutral-bgAlt border border-neutral-border p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm space-y-6 text-center">
          <!-- Icon Amplop / Mail -->
          <div class="inline-flex p-3.5 bg-primary/10 rounded-full text-primary border border-primary/20">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-8 h-8">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21.75 6.75v10.5a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25 2.25h-15a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25-2.25V6.75m19.5 0A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 19.5 4.5h-15a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-2.25 2.25m19.5 0v.243a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-1.07 1.916l-7.5 4.615a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.36 0L3.32 8.91a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-1.07-1.916V6.75" />
            </svg>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-2">
            <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-neutral-text">Alamat Email Resmi</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-neutral-textMuted max-w-xs mx-auto">
              Silakan kirimkan pesan Anda secara langsung ke alamat email developer berikut:
            </p>
            <div class="bg-neutral-bg px-4 py-2.5 rounded border border-neutral-border inline-block font-mono text-sm text-primary select-all select-none">
              irfansyarifudin79@gmail.com
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Tombol Kirim Email -->
          <div class="pt-2">
            <a
              href="mailto:irfansyarifudin79@gmail.com?subject=Tanya%20Cek%20Kebocoran%20Data"
              class="inline-flex items-center space-x-2 py-3 px-6 bg-primary hover:bg-primary-dark text-white font-semibold rounded-md transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:ring-offset-2 w-full sm:w-auto justify-center text-sm"
              aria-label="Kirim Email ke irfansyarifudin79@gmail.com"
            >
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 12 3.269 3.125A59.769 59.769 0 0 1 21.485 12 59.768 59.768 0 0 1 3.27 20.875L5.999 12Zm0 0h7.5" />
              </svg>
              <span>Kirim Email Sekarang</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Tambahan / Petunjuk FAQ -->
        <p class="text-xs text-neutral-textMuted text-center leading-relaxed">
          Sebelum menghubungi kami, Anda juga bisa membaca halaman <a href="/faq" class="text-primary hover:underline font-medium">FAQ (Pertanyaan Umum)</a> kami untuk menemukan jawaban cepat dari pertanyaan-pertanyaan yang sering diajukan.
        </p>

      </section>
    </article>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>
